title: We Are Freestyle
description:
We may not play the same sport or have the same passions, we may not have the same gender, religion or faith, we may not live in the same country, city, or state, but we all spend our days breathing, bleeding and sweating the same way. At the end of the day it’s all about performance and together we are Freestyle, we are performance timing.
Visit freestyleusa.com for full product details.
Special Thanks:
Marc Beaty at Surfline
Jameson Walter
Tyler Malay
Alexandra Erickson
Ian Post (I Heart Snow)

Fuel TV

Panasonic HVX200
Canon XHA1
Canon HV30
